This compendium, though ostensibly a complete roster, is, as explicitly noted, [incomplete](/Wikipedia:WikiProject_Lists); one can always attempt to improve it by adding the missing fragments of history, a Sisyphean task if ever there was one. (Last updated, or perhaps merely glanced at, in June 2019.)

What follows is a comprehensive, if somewhat exhaustive, catalogue of individuals who have served as members of the [New York State Senate](/New_York_State_Senate), spanning from its inception to the present day. Those members who were actively serving in the [Senate](/New_York_State_Senate) as of July 2022 are, for reasons of contemporary relevance, visually distinguished, though such fleeting distinctions rarely alter the fundamental nature of their contributions.

***

